      "text": "The participants should leave after a session (or after a seminar day) with a feeling of accomplishment. They should know exactly what they have learned and what they can do with that knowledge. Sometimes, the important parts get lost in the details that have been discussed during the session or day. Always make sure that the participants can identify the important topics. These topics should be embedded in a greater context. This facilitates the transfer of the knowledge into long term memory.\n  ",
      "id": "24c9c9c2eefea19d",
